    FROM (
        SELECT 
            res.milliseconds,
            ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY res.raceId ORDER BY res.position) AS position_rank,
            COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY res.raceId) AS total_positions
        FROM races r 
        JOIN results res ON r.raceId = res.raceId 
        JOIN drivers d ON res.driverId = d.driverId 
        WHERE r.year = 2008 AND r.name = 'Australian Grand Prix' AND res.TIME IS NOT NULL
    ) ranked_results
    WHERE position_rank = 1 OR position_rank = total_positions
) AS subquery;
